er%20they'd%20be%20willing%20to%20move%20closer%20to%20Manhattan%20to%20shorten%20his%20commute%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decision%20that%20could%20mean%20breaking%20their%20lease%20before%20it%20ended%20the%20following%20August%2C%20finding%20a%20new%20home%2C%20and%20enrolling%20their%20daughter%20in%20a%20new%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227db4a6ba-1eb2-475d-ad73-5b6567564551%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%94%20and%20trying%20to%20move%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Telemarque%20weighed%20his%20options%2C%20he%20said%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20September%2015%20decision%20deadline%20was%20approaching%20fast.%20He%20struggled%20to%20get%20comfortable%20with%20the%20lifestyle%20adjustments%20a%20five-day%20commute%20would%20require%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20could%20make%20it%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20logistics%2C%20Telemarque%20said%20he%20also%20felt%20uneasy%20about%20the%20direction%20Paramount%20was%20heading%20under%20its%20new%20leadership.%20He%20found%20it%20somewhat%20frustrating%20that%20he%20had%20performed%20well%20enough%20to%20earn%20a%20promotion%20in%20a%20hybrid%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20yet%20couldn't%20retain%20that%20flexibility%20under%20the%20company's%20new%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20severance%20package%20and%20leave%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20have%20enough%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20my%20best%20bet%20was%20to%20take%20the%20package.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETelemarque%20said%20he%20worked%20through%20the%20end%20of%20October%20before%20officially%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20company%20and%20turning%20his%20attention%20to%20finding%20his%20next%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Telemarque%20has%20been%20targeting%20roles%20related%20to%20strategy%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20distribution%20within%20the%20media%20and%20entertainment%20