inessinsider.com%2Fmicro-dramas-reelshort-dramabox-billion-dollar-business-in-us-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emicro%20drama%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20has%20added%20a%20section%20where%20you%20can%20binge%20on%C2%A0bite-sized%20series%20without%20leaving%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TikTok%20Minis%20section%20features%20%26quot%3Blightweight%2C%20in-app%20mini%20programs%20that%20let%20users%20access%20experiences%20and%20content%20without%20leaving%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20TikTok%20staffer%20recently%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn.%20That%20tab%20has%20both%20%26quot%3Bmini%20games%26quot%3B%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20apps%20for%20%26quot%3Bmini%20dramas%2C%26quot%3B%20otherwise%20known%20as%20micro%20dramas%20or%20verticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20boost%20for%20these%20low-budget%2C%20made-for-mobile%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20movie-length%20soapy%20titles%20chopped%20into%20short%20episodes%20%E2%80%94%20that%20grew%20out%20of%20China%20and%20have%20gained%20popularity%20in%20the%20US.%20Plots%20often%20revolve%20around%20tropes%20like%20badly%20behaving%20husbands%20or%20werewolf%20romance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20format%20may%20reduce%20early-funnel%20friction%20by%20letting%20audiences%20sample%20episodes%20inside%20TikTok%20before%20any%20off-platform%20step%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TikTok%20staffer%20wrote%20of%20the%20TikTok%20Minis%20program.%20The%20post%20is%20no%20longer%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20who%20has%20privately%20discussed%20the%20Minis%20program%20with%20TikTok%20said%20the%20company%20views%20it%20as%20a%20way%20to%20build%20on%20its%20success%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-shop-one-of-the-fastest-growing-brands-this-year-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20Shop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20established%20itself%20as%20a%20major%20social%20commerce%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20TikTok%20exec%20Jerry%20Soer%20post%20on%20Linkedin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6949adb104eda4732f2dff4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETikTok%20exec%20Jerry%20Soer%20recently%20posted%20about%20the%20feature%20on%20LinkedIn.%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20drama%20apps%20mostly%20operate%20on%20a%20freemium%20model%2C%20where%20users%20are%20prompted%20to%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20often%20%2410%20or%20more%20per%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20after%20watching%20about%20eight%20to%2010%20episodes.%20They%20also%20often%20offer%20subscriptions%2C%20which%20can%20run%20%2440%20to%20%2480%20a%20month%2C%20for%20unlimited%20viewing.%20With%20TikTok%20Minis%2C%20there's%20a%20wrinkle%3A%20There's%20often%20a%2010%25%20discount%20that%20incentivizes%20viewers%20to%20stay%20within%20the%20TikTok%20app%20rather%20than%20click%20away%20to%20the%20short%20drama%20app%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Minis%20feature%20could%20appeal%20to%20lesser-known%20apps%20that%20hope%20to%20use%20TikTok's%20massive%20audience%20to%20grow%20their%20reach.%20Those%20with%20well-established%20audiences%20may%20prefer%20to%20keep%20them%20on%20their%20own%20platforms%2C%20where%20they%20can%20control%20monetization.%20Notably%2C%20the%20two%20biggest%20players%2C%20ReelShort%20and%20DramaBox%2C%20aren't%20represented%20in%20the%20Minis%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20also%20encouraged%20short%20drama%20makers%20to%20use%20its%20%26quot%3Bseries%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20which%20lets%20them%20add%20paywalled%20videos%20to%20their%20TikTok%20accounts.%20ReelShort%20and%20the%20fast-growing%20Netshort%20are%20among%20those%20using%20that%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245869677-b583-4f49-8617-9d3d9a186b40%5C%22%3ETikTok%20has%20pitched%20micro%20drama%20producers%20on%20making%20their%20offerings%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20two%20micro%20drama%20producers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20TikTok%20pitched%20them%20on%20sharing%20full%2C%20original%20episodes%20on%20the%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20unpaywalled%20%E2%80%94%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20share%20of%20ad%20revenue.%20One%20of%20them%20said%20TikTok%20offered%20to%20pay%20a%20licensing%20fee%20(up%20to%20%2410%2C000%20for%20an%20original%20series)%20plus%20a%20share%20of%20ad%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20producers%20expressed%20doubts%20that%20the%20economics%20of%20TikTok's%20revenue-sharing%20proposal%2C%20which%20would%20represent%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20their%20business%20model%2C%20would%20be%20effective.%20In%20theory%2C%20the%20Minis%20section%20could%20help%20expose%20micro%20dramas%20to%20new%20audiences%20and%20lower%20their%20marketing%20costs.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20unclear%20whether%20the%20licensing%20and%20unspecified%20ad%20revenue%20would%20cover%20the%20production%20costs%2C%20which%20typically%20range%20from%20%24100%2C000%20to%20%24300%2C000%20for%20a%20full-length%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20third%20verticals%20producer%2C%20Thom%20Woodley%2C%20said%20the%20Minis%20section%20could%20help%20provide%20an%20on-ramp%20for%20Westerners%20who%20might%20not%20want%20to%20leave%20the%20platform%20for%20an%20app%20they've%20never%20heard%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPaying%20via%20TikTok%2C%20with%20subscriptions%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20something%20that%20people%20may%20trust%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicro%20dramas%20aren't%20new%20to%20TikTok's%20owner%2C%20ByteDance.%20TikTok's%20Chinese%20counterpart%2C%20Douyin%2C%20introduced%20vertical%20dramas%20to%20its%20platform%2C%20and%20ByteDance%20has%20its%20own%20vertical%20drama%20app%20called%20Melolo.%20(After%20a%20drawn-out%20ownership%20limbo%2C%20TikTok%20recently%20reached%20an%20agreement%20through%20which%20it%20will%20avoid%20a%20ban%20by%20getting%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-could-take-over-tiktok-us-business-investors-oracle-ellison-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20cohort%20of%20US%20part-owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20a%20joint%20venture.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTikTok's%20parent%20company%20was%20instrumental%20in%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20format%20in%20China%2C%20and%20they%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20happens%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hernan%20Lopez%2C%20founder%20of%20streaming%20consulting%20firm%20Owl%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20micro%20drama%20producers%20said%20that%20if%20TikTok%20succeeds%20in%20transitioning%20micro%20dramas%20to%20a%20non-paywalled%20model%20and%20shifting%20viewing%20to%20its%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20as%20ByteDance%20has%20done%20in%20China%20%E2%80%94%20it%20could%20reorder%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShort-drama%20apps%20are%20on%20track%20to%20make%20%243%20billion%20in%20revenue%20this%20year%20globally%20(excluding%20China)%2C%20nearly%20triple%20the%20year%20before%2C%20Owl%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20estimated.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-invests-micro-dramas-disney-fox-explore-the-format-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHollywood%20establishment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Big%20Tech%20are%20taking%20note%20as%20they%20seek%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20audience%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20big%20move%20by%20a%20Hollywood%20studio%2C%20Fox%20invested%20in%20Holywater%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20company%20behind%20the%20micro%20drama%20app%20My%20Drama.%20Disney%20said%20last%20month%20it's%20in%20talks%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdramabox-strategy-to-dominate-us-micro-dramas-creators-disney-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicro%20drama%20app%20DramaBox%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20adapt%20young%20adult%20fantasy%20novels%20into%20original%20microdramas%20for%20its%20media%20platforms%20and%20is%20exploring%20adapting%20music%20albums%20into