suddenly%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20I%20had%20to%20sort%20through%20a%20tangled%20mess%20of%20finances%20that%20she%20had%20accumulated.%20Her%20home%20was%20also%20in%20a%20state%20of%20disarray.%20It%20was%20clearly%20no%20longer%20safe%20for%20her%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-small-mobile-home-independence-freedom-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20living%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20away%2C%20busy%20with%20our%20toddler%20and%20a%20new%20baby.%20Since%20my%20mom%20was%20single%2C%20with%20no%20other%20family%20members%20nearby%20except%20my%20brother%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-brother-with-down-syndrome-just-became-my-housemate-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDown%20Syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20simply%20no%20one%20who%20could%20help.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20deer%20in%20headlights%2C%20alone%20with%20no%20idea%20where%20to%20start%2C%20and%20with%20the%20caregiving%20weight%20of%20small%20children%20and%20now%20aging%20and%20disabled%20adults%20on%20my%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anna%20De%20La%20Cruz%20mother%20and%20brother.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6944302104eda4732f2dc978%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20mother%20and%20brother.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anna%20De%20La%20Cruz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20hours%20on%20research%20and%20tours%3B%20I%20did%20my%20best%20to%20find%20my%20mother%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanage-senior-home-moving-in-was-the-best-decision-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eassisted%20living%20facility%3C%2Fa%3E%20closer%20to%20me%20that%20seemed%20to%20offer%20what%20we%20needed%20at%20a%20price%20point%20that%20she%